room_title: Escape room "Bank Robbery" by Fox in a Box Tucson in Tucson
room_description: You are a group of well-informed thieves. It has come to your attention that the general manager of Tucson City Bank has a stash of diamonds hidden in his office. In the dark of the night, you managed to sneak into the bank and reached the office of the CEO's secretary. From there, you deactivated the alarm, but it will sound off in exactly one hour. If you get to the diamonds in time, you will be rich beyond your wildest dreams. Fail, and you will end your career behind bars.
